<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (tẖbt ạ̉nẓạrk fyh .. wḥmwlk sybhạ ʿlyh)2
 (wfy wạdy ẓl ạlmwt)2 .. (ạ̹rfʿ ʿynk tlạqyh)2
 1- (ạ̹n knt smʿt ndạh .. ʿ ạlmyẗ msẖyt wyạh)2
 (lyh ttlft ḥwạlyk)2 .. (ʿynk kẖlyhạ ʿlyh)2
 2- (ạ̹n sẖft bʿynk nạr .. ṣdq yṭfyhạ ạlbạr)2
 (ạ̉w jwạhạ ymsẖyk)2 .. (zy ạlftyạn ḥwạlyh)2
 3- (ạ̹n knt fy wqt ạ̉lym .. ḥwạlyk ạlsẖr ʿẓym)2
 (ạ̹ymạnk bạlly fạdyk)2 .. (gẖạlb lw ttẖbt fyh)2
 4- (ạ̹n knt fy sẖdẗ wḍyq .. wạ̹n fạtk ạ̉ʿz ṣdyq)2
 (fyh wạḥd ạ̹smh yswʿ)2 .. (mạsk ạ̹ydk fy ạ̹ydyh)2</lyrics>
<title>tẖbt ạ̉nẓạrk fyh</title>
